parameters:
\SE[2]This is... a document storage room...? \SE[3]Why... am
I in a place like this...?

\SE[2]Is there something... that Vega wants to show me
here...?

\SE[2]Yes... but, \SE[3]I don't know the exact location.
[2]Could you help me search for it? It should be a stack
of documents.
\SE[102]C-Can we find something from within here...?

\SE[20]I-it should be here... \SE[91]It's something very
important, so we have to find it somehow...

\SE[16]It's okay! It's okay! Let's do our best together,
okay? \SE[0]Right?
Let's try to find the documents that should be here!
\SE[2]What kind of things should I search for?

\SE[2]It shouldn't be in the shape of a book. \!\SE[3]It
might be a bundle of papers... or maybe it's in an
envelope...

\SE[14]It's not that I'm hiding it... If I were hiding it...
Would it be behind the bookshelf... or something...?
\SE[3]Hmm... Maybe not... That's what I would do though...

\SE[2]This is a psychological battle, right? \!\SE[15]If you
can read the hidden person's heart, you can win.
\SE[2]At a time like this, it's something trivial, but...
\SE[8]This clock... for some reason, it feels... off.

\SE[5]Ah... The hour hand and minute hand are misaligned...?
\SE[3]The minute hand is almost at 12, but the hour hand is
not catching up at all.

\SE[4]Ah... That's why it felt strange.... \SE[15]I wonder
what it is... It's making me restless.... \SE[17]I want to
fix it right away....

\SE[98]Let's do it...! \.It's the fault of this wrong
clock...!

\SE[15]Yeah, that's right.... \.I want this clock to keep
the correct time...\.it should....

\SE[46]Ah... The clock is completely shattered... I'm
sorry.... \SE[65]I didn't mean for this to happen....

\SE[78]Hey, what are you guys playing? \!\SE[4]...Wait, this
is...

\SE[2]I wonder if this is... a catalog of prisoners' crimes?
\SE[3]There are various types of crimes, aren't there...
\SE[38]... Oh, I can't. \SE[3] I need to focus...

She is reading through the documents at an incredible
speed... It seems better not to disturb her...

I tried putting it back in its original position for now...
The damage is so bad that things like the angle of the
needle don't even matter.

\SE[99]What is this place...? \!\SE[5]Wow, there are so
many restraints... \!\SE[99]Handcuffs, ankle cuffs... and a
blindfold...?
\SE[53]I need to hide before Lunaroa finds me...

\SE[2]This is... food, right? It seems like there are better
ingredients than I expected... \SE[3]I wonder if rice can be
surprisingly good...?

\SE[3]I see. So this is a facility for reflection. It's
meaningless if it's not healthy, right?
\SE[93]Hmm... It seems like it's not here.

\SE[102]U-uh... so many books... \SE[51]I'm not good with
this kind of thing, so I'll leave it to those two...
